metadata.name: the marblr statue
metadata.description:
The Marble statue
Concept/photo: Thanit KG
man and woman There are different shapes that have been created. It was God who created beauty, that all the sculptures that were formed were modeled by human beings. I really want to convey the meaning of sculpture by using human beings. It's a message that These guys of all genders can communicate with each other. It's not about the species, although they are different. can understand each other merged into one another
